    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit exhibits strong compression across all cylinders and a smooth power delivery characteristic of its individual throttle body setup. The VANOS system has been professionally serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known structural pain point\u2014has been reinforced for long-term chassis rigidity. It utilizes a Getrag six-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque vectoring and driver engagement. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the suspension bushings and dampers remain tight, offering the sharp turn-in and balanced handling these M-cars are celebrated for. A well-maintained example ready for the twisties or daily spirited driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
