    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 Lexus RX 350 is a well-maintained luxury SUV that perfectly balances performance and comfort. The Atomic Silver exterior retains a beautiful luster, with only minor road-wear chips on the front bumper and a small, professionally touched-up scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple Parchment leather; while the driver\u2019s seat shows light bolster creasing, the remaining seats appear nearly new. All power features, including the panoramic sunroof and dual-zone climate control, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is in great shape with a consistent service history; the V6 engine runs quietly, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. It currently sits on a set of premium all-season tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
