    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic car for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. I've taken good care of it, and it's ready for its next adventure with you. Come take it for a spin, I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
