    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 powered by the legendary 4.0L S65 V8, an atmospheric powerhouse featuring individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This example utilizes a 6-speed manual transmission paired with a variable M-differential lock for maximum mechanical engagement. The chassis architecture remains sharp, featuring M-specific aluminum subframes and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) to manage transient weight transfer. Recent service includes rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the high-revving internals are protected. While the exterior shows minor signs of spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response remain exceptionally crisp.",
